OL,6,FUK Editor Paul Brand speaks to Megan
OL,7,FRoyal whose mother travelled to
OL,8,FSwitzerland to end her life without
OL,9,Ftelling her family
OL,11,FA family from Ireland found out via
OL,12,FWhatsApp that their mother had died
OL,13,Fafter travelling to an assisted dying
OL,14,Fclinic in Switzerland.
OL,16,FMaureen Slough, 58, travelled to the
OL,17,FPegasos clinic in July, where her
OL,18,Ffamily say she was helped to take her
OL,19,Fown life in secret.
