OL,3,CFamily found out via WhatsApp that
OL,4,Cmother took her life at Swiss clinic
OL,6,FHer daughter Megan Royal told ITV News
OL,7,Fthat her mother had not informed
OL,8,Fanyone of her intentions before flying
OL,9,Fto Basel.
OL,11,FThe first they heard of her death was
OL,12,Fvia a WhatsApp message from the clinic
OL,13,Fsent shortly afterwards on July 10,
OL,14,Fstating: "Maureen passed away
OL,15,Fpeacefully today at 1303 Swiss local
OL,16,Ftime.
