OL,3,CFamily found out via WhatsApp that
OL,4,Cmother took her life at Swiss clinic
OL,6,F"She was not alone and she was
OL,7,Fembraced by a Pegasos nurse, attendant
OL,8,Fand dog altogether (sic)... She
OL,9,Frequested Elvis Gospel music to be
OL,10,Fplayed."
OL,12,FMaureen had no known terminal illness
OL,13,Fand her daughter says she was
OL,14,Fstruggling with the grief of recently
OL,15,Flosing her two sisters.
OL,17,F"She was having a bad time, not a bad
OL,18,Flife," Megan told us. "A cannula isn't
OL,19,Fthe way, you just need someone to give
OL,20,Fyou a hug and feel supported."
