OL,6,FMaureen had only just become a
OL,7,Fgrandmother to a baby girl, born weeks
OL,8,Fbefore she died.
OL,10,F"When I got the message, I was just
OL,11,Fholding my newborn and trying my best
OL,12,Fnot to break," Megan said.
OL,14,F"I actually replied to Pegasos asking
OL,15,F'Where is my mum? Who are you?' I got
OL,16,Fa bit angry and they blocked me."
OL,18,FMaureen's ashes were eventually posted
OL,19,Fhome several weeks later.
