OL,3,CFamily found out via WhatsApp that
OL,4,Cmother took her life at Swiss clinic
OL,6,F"She was sent back with a tracking
OL,7,Fnumber," Megan says. "Like getting an
OL,8,FAmazon delivery, but only Amazon are
OL,9,Fquicker."
OL,11,FMegan has been unable to recover her
OL,12,Fmother's phone or access her messages.
OL,14,FPegasos told us that in cases where
OL,15,Fsomeone is unaccompanied to their
OL,16,Fclinic, "the deceased person's mobile
OL,17,Fphone is reset to factory settings",
OL,18,Fmeaning nothing can be accessed after
OL,19,Ftheir death.
