OL,6,FMaureen's family are the latest to
OL,7,Ftell ITV News that their loved one
OL,8,Fdisappeared to Pegasos without warning.
OL,10,FIn 2023, Alastair Hamilton flew to
OL,11,FSwitzerland to end his life at the
OL,12,Fclinic without telling his mother or
OL,13,Fbrothers.
OL,15,FIn May 2024, ITV News helped his
OL,16,Ffamily trace his final steps to an
OL,17,Findustrial estate outside Basel, where
OL,18,Fhe was assisted to die alone.
