OL,6,FAnd in January 2025, Anne Canning made
OL,7,Fthe same trip without telling her
OL,8,Ffamily.
OL,10,FAssisted dying is legal in
OL,11,FSwitzerland, where there are very few
OL,12,Frestrictions and almost anyone can end
OL,13,Ftheir own life as long as the person
OL,14,Fassisting them isn't driven by selfish
OL,15,Fmotives.
OL,17,FPegasos has repeatedly promised to
OL,18,Fchange its procedures to ensure that
OL,19,Fits clients inform a relative before
OL,20,Fbeing helped to take their own life.
