OL,6,FThe clinic claims that it received a
OL,7,Fletter from Megan giving her blessing
OL,8,Fto her mother's decision, which they
OL,9,Fsay was also verified via email.
OL,11,FHowever, Megan insists that she never
OL,12,Fwrote a letter or any email and
OL,13,Fsuspects that her mother may have
OL,14,Fforged both.
OL,16,FAfter 18 months investigating the
OL,17,Fclinic, concerns are now being voiced
OL,18,Fby legislators in Switzerland about
OL,19,Fthe increased use of assisted dying
OL,20,Fclinics by foreign clients.
