OL,6,FPegasos is not accused of breaking any
OL,7,FSwiss law, but some Swiss politicians
OL,8,Fare now questioning whether tighter
OL,9,Fregulation is required.
OL,11,FHeidi Z'graggen, a member of
OL,12,FSwitzerland's Council of States,
OL,13,Frecently raised the issue in
OL,14,Fparliament.
OL,16,F"In recent years, the number of
OL,17,Fassisted suicides has increased
OL,18,Fcontinuously," she said.
