OL,9,Fthe last two years. We decided to no
OL,10,Flonger accept unaccompanied applicants
OL,11,Fwith living family members unless we
OL,12,Fwill be provided with copies of their
OL,13,Fpassports and will be able to meet
OL,14,Fthem in a video call."
